<div class="about-container">
<h1>Our Services</h1>
<!-- background/image on the side: screengrab from Dahlapalooza, parallax scroll? -->
<p class="about-text">Rare Visions provides an immersive light show rooted in analog liquid light
    projections from the 1960s and infused with
    modern visual aesthetics such as glitch art and video synthesis.  Projections are
    improvised live in response to music and the surrounding environment, producing a 
    unique and hypnotic psychedelic backdrop to concerts and events.
</p>
